text: Dobell is a surname. Notable people with the surname include *Charles Macpherson Dobell (1869–1954), Canadian soldier *Clifford Dobell (1886–1949), British biologist *Doug Dobell (1917–1987), British record store proprietor and record producer *Eva Dobell (1867–1963), British poet, nurse, and editor *Horace Dobell (c. 1827 – 1917), English doctor and medical writer *Richard Reid Dobell (1836–1902), Canadian businessman and politician *Sydney Thompson Dobell (1824–1874), English poet and critic *William Dobell (1899–1970), Australian artist == See also == *Dobell Prize, prize for drawing in Australia *Division of Dobell, an Australian electoral Division in New South Wales
